<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ومن قال عن اثنين:</span> <span class="c1">"أحدُهما زانٍ"</span>،<span class="c5"> فقال أحدُهما:</span> <span class="c1">"أنا؟ "</span>،<span class="c5"> فقال:</span> <span class="c1">"لا"</span>، فقذفٌ للآخَرِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">و:</span> <span class="c1">"زنأْتِ"</span>، مهموزًا، صريحٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>،<span class="c5"> ولو زاد:</span> <span class="c1">"في الجَبَل <span class="c2">(٣)</span>، أو عُرْفِ العربية"</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>* * *<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
